data.description: Once in a lifetime opportunity to make your dream home a reality. Live on Holiday 365 days a year. " Don't Worry, Be Happy " Every little thing has been done for you.  Your Sanctuary comes professionally designed and  decorated. Two Bedrooms.  Two Bathrooms.  Two Decks. Gated Community. All New Genuine Hardwood Flooring. Custom Real Wood Plantation Shutters.  Modern quartz Countertops Throughout. High Unique Architectural Ceiling. Imported Italian Title in Both Showers. Designer High End Furniture Pieces Throughout. New Sterns and Foster Adjustable Base with massage Feature Bed. Hand Blown Light Fixtures. Two New Top Grain Leather Custom Lazy Boy Recliners. New Custom Designer Fabric Lazy Boy Love Seat. Pool and Spa. Garage. Five minutes to the Ocean. Close to all Shopping and Restaurants. All New double Low E Windows. Samsung Washer and Dryer.  All New Stainless Steel Whirlpool appliances. Double Oven. Gas Cook Top. Moen Fixtures.  Under Sink Water Filtration. Custom Cabinets through out.  65" LG TV in living room.  55" Samsung TV with Nakmichi Sound System.  New Water Heater. Both Bathrooms Totally Remodeled. The whole house has been Professionally Remodeled. The Garage has even been remodeled with Epoxy floor and New Lift Mast Garage door Opener.
